'''尼古劳斯·西姆羅克音樂出版社'''（{{lang-de|'''Musikverlag Nikolaus Simrock'''}}，經常簡記為N. Simrock、Simrock Verlag，或僅以其姓氏Simrock表示）是一家德國的樂譜出版社，1793年由{{link-de|尼古劳斯·西姆羅克|Nikolaus Simrock}}創建於[[波昂|波昂]]。在[[沃尔夫冈·阿马德乌斯·莫扎特|莫扎特]]、[[约瑟夫·海顿|海頓]]、[[路德维希·范·贝多芬|貝多芬]]、[[费利克斯·门德尔松·巴托尔迪|门德尔松]]、[[罗伯特·舒曼|舒曼]]、[[约翰内斯·勃拉姆斯|勃拉姆斯]]、[[马克斯·布鲁赫|布鲁赫]]、[[安东宁·德沃夏克|德弗乍克]]、[[约瑟夫·苏克_(作曲家)|苏克]]等19世紀德、奧作曲家作品方面，是具公信力的出版源之一。

== 沿革 ==
19世紀期間，其業務在尼古劳斯之子彼得·約瑟夫（Peter Joseph）以及第三代{{link-de|弗里茨·西姆羅克|Fritz Simrock|弗里茨}}的經營下有所成長。1870年，總部遷移至[[柏林|柏林]]<ref>Donald William Krummel and Stanley Sadie, ''Music Printing and Publishing'', Norton/Grove handbooks in music, New York: Norton, 1990, {{ISBN|9780393028096}}, [https://books.google.com/books?ei=PMGgT-24B8eRiALHuOTVAg&id=UcoXAQAAIAAJ&dq=Richard+Schauer%2C+Anton+J.+Benjamin&q=Simrock#search_anchor p. 107] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?ei=PMGgT-24B8eRiALHuOTVAg&id=UcoXAQAAIAAJ&dq=Richard+Schauer%2C+Anton+J.+Benjamin&q=Simrock#search_anchor |date=20170410235712 }}.</ref>，由弗里茨的姪輩漢斯（Hans）負責營運。

[[File:Simrock_Dvorak_5.jpg|thumb]][[第9號交響曲_(德沃夏克)|《新世界》交響曲]]鋼琴改編版的封面，1906年]]
1907年，他們收購了萊比錫的Bartholf Senff{{譯名請求}}<ref name=Biba89>Otto Biba, "Die Simrocks—Verleger für Beethoven wie für Brahms", in ''Johannes Brahms und Bonn'', ed. Martella Gutiérrez-Denhoff, Bonn: Stadt Bonn, Beethoven-Haus, 1997, {{ISBN|9783922832164}}, [https://books.google.com/books?id=ZrQHAQAAMAAJ&q=Musikverlag+Simrock&dq=Musikverlag+Simrock&hl=en&sa=X&ei=0KyeT_mSKOXjiALDraRQ&ved=0CFwQ6AEwBw p. 89] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=ZrQHAQAAMAAJ&q=Musikverlag+Simrock&dq=Musikverlag+Simrock&hl=en&sa=X&ei=0KyeT_mSKOXjiALDraRQ&ved=0CFwQ6AEwBw |date=20210216084357 }} {{de}}</ref><ref>''Beiträge zur Geschichte des Buchwesens'' 3 (1968) [https://books.google.com/books?ei=wUegT43QN4nYiAL10uzCAg&id=nsNMAQAAIAAJ&dq=%22Ahn+%26+Simrock%22+1911+%22N.+Simrock%22&q=N.+Simrock#search_anchor p. 204] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?ei=wUegT43QN4nYiAL10uzCAg&id=nsNMAQAAIAAJ&dq=%22Ahn+%26+Simrock%22+1911+%22N.+Simrock%22&q=N.+Simrock#search_anchor |date=20170410231302 }} {{de}}</ref>。1911年曾短暫與阿爾伯特·安（Albert Ahn）合併，易名為「安與西姆羅克」，而後又再次拆夥。1929年，轉而由安東·班傑明（Anton Benjamin）收購<ref name=Biba89/><ref>''The School Musician Director and Teacher'' 56 (1985) [https://books.google.com/books?ei=5EmgT4z_CaqRiAK6ra2CAg&id=pePjAAAAMAAJ&dq=N.+Simrock+Anton+J.+Benjamin&q=The+Hamburg+firm+of+Anton+J.+Benjamin%2C+founded+in+1818%2C+acquired+the+catalog+of+Daniel+Rahter+in+1917%2C+and+the+great+catalog+of+N.+Simrock+in+1929%2C+thus+inheriting+a+tradition+including+the+original+editions+of+Beethoven%2C+Brahms%2C+Bruch#search_anchor p. 42] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?ei=5EmgT4z_CaqRiAK6ra2CAg&id=pePjAAAAMAAJ&dq=N.+Simrock+Anton+J.+Benjamin&q=The+Hamburg+firm+of+Anton+J.+Benjamin%2C+founded+in+1818%2C+acquired+the+catalog+of+Daniel+Rahter+in+1917%2C+and+the+great+catalog+of+N.+Simrock+in+1929%2C+thus+inheriting+a+tradition+including+the+original+editions+of+Beethoven%2C+Brahms%2C+Bruch#search_anchor |date=20210327152137 }}.</ref><ref name=GeschichteuGegenwart>Ludwig Finscher and Friedrich Blume, ''Die Musik in Geschichte und Gegenwart: allgemeine Enzyklopädie der Musik'', Part 2, Volume 15, Kassel: [[貝倫賴特出版社|Bärenreiter]], 2006, {{ISBN|9783476410306}}, [https://books.google.com/books?ei=JM-gT5arKdHQiAKF0ujWAg&id=3LkzAQAAIAAJ&dq=Boosey+%26+Hawkes%2C+Simrock%2C+Benjamin%2C+2002&q=1929+wurde+N.+Simrock+an+den+Musikverlag+Anton+J.+Benjamin+in+Leipzig+verkauft%2C+aber+unter+altem+Namen+weitergef%C3%BChrt.+Im+Zuge+der+%3EArisierung%3C+...+2002+gelangte+N.+Simrock+durch+den+Verkauf+des+Verlages+Benjamin+an+Boosey+%26+Hawkes#search_anchor p. 837] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?ei=JM-gT5arKdHQiAKF0ujWAg&id=3LkzAQAAIAAJ&dq=Boosey+%26+Hawkes%2C+Simrock%2C+Benjamin%2C+2002&q=1929+wurde+N.+Simrock+an+den+Musikverlag+Anton+J.+Benjamin+in+Leipzig+verkauft%2C+aber+unter+altem+Namen+weitergef%C3%BChrt.+Im+Zuge+der+%3EArisierung%3C+...+2002+gelangte+N.+Simrock+durch+den+Verkauf+des+Verlages+Benjamin+an+Boosey+%26+Hawkes#search_anchor |date=20170410235631 }} {{de}}</ref>{{notetag|安東·班傑明出版社於1951年重組，2002年再由[[博浩出版社|博浩出版社]]收購<ref name=GeschichteuGegenwart/>。}}。

[[二次大戰|二次大戰]]期間，許多藏譜和印刷用版不幸在戰事中遭到波及，許多舊版本的樂譜因此絕版，再製不易<ref>''The Instrumentalist'' 47 (1992) [https://books.google.com/books?id=_DhLAAAAYAAJ&q=N.+Simrock+Anton+J.+Benjamin&dq=N.+Simrock+Anton+J.+Benjamin&hl=en&sa=X&ei=5EmgT4z_CaqRiAK6ra2CAg&ved=0CFgQ6AEwBg pp. 5, 106] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=_DhLAAAAYAAJ&q=N.+Simrock+Anton+J.+Benjamin&dq=N.+Simrock+Anton+J.+Benjamin&hl=en&sa=X&ei=5EmgT4z_CaqRiAK6ra2CAg&ved=0CFgQ6AEwBg |date=20170410235213 }}.</ref>。目前，大部分的西姆羅克史料皆藏於萊比錫的萨克森邦資料館（Saxon State Archive），當中部分的資料在1990年至2000年期間轉移至他處<ref>Michael Freyhan, ''The Authentic Magic Flute Libretto: Mozart's Autograph Or the First Full Score Edition?'', Lanham, Maryland: Scarecrow, 2009, {{ISBN|9780810869677}}, [https://books.google.com/books?id=aZRiQ3eDnqAC&pg=PA159&dq=Simrock+Archive+Leipzig&hl=en&sa=X&ei=aKWhT-ahMtLSiALJiI22Bw&ved=0CDUQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=Simrock%20Archive%20Leipzig&f=false p. 159] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=aZRiQ3eDnqAC&pg=PA159&dq=Simrock+Archive+Leipzig&hl=en&sa=X&ei=aKWhT-ahMtLSiALJiI22Bw&ved=0CDUQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=Simrock%20Archive%20Leipzig&f=false |date=20170410232949 }}.</ref>。

== 特色 ==
承前，西姆羅克出版社占地利之便，在當代的德、奧音樂出版領域有不可忽視的權威性。他們是最早推出「原典版本」（考究作者本人意圖的編輯版樂譜）的音樂出版社之一。莫扎特《[[魔笛|魔笛]]》<ref>Freyhan, [https://books.google.com/books?id=uBYI_8RM2BoC&pg=PA68&dq=%22Simrock+sold%22&hl=en&sa=X&ei=e9GgT9miDcGeiAKZ3p2yAg&ved=0CDUQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=%22Simrock%20sold%22&f=false p. 68, note 51] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=uBYI_8RM2BoC&pg=PA68&dq=%22Simrock+sold%22&hl=en&sa=X&ei=e9GgT9miDcGeiAKZ3p2yAg&ved=0CDUQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=%22Simrock%20sold%22&f=false |date=20170410235805 }}.</ref>、舒曼第3號交響曲、門德爾松《[[以利亞_(孟德爾遜)|以利亞]]》與《保羅》<ref name="Bonn">{{cite web |title=Nikolaus Simrock |url=http://www2.bonn.de/stadtmuseum/inhalte/n_simrock.htm |accessdate=2012-05-01 |year=2012 |publisher=Stadtmuseum Bonn |language=de |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120427141324/http://www2.bonn.de/stadtmuseum/inhalte/n_simrock.htm |archivedate=2012-04-27 }}</ref>、布魯赫[[第1小提琴协奏曲_(布鲁赫)|第1號小提琴協奏曲]]等作品，因該社的編輯工作而得以有可信的樂譜版本傳世。

